# Local Claude Code state (launch.json, settings.local.json, etc.) stays ignored, but
# committed project skills under .claude/skills/ and subagent definitions under
# .claude/agents/ are tracked so they ship with the repo.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/agents/
# Design WORKING files stay local: raw inspiration, teaware source shots, and the
# .dc.html standalone exports (~10MB each of inlined runtime). The LOCKED R3 record
# lives in docs/r3/ and IS committed — it's the spec Code builds from, not reference.
SlowCup R2 bundle handoff/
design-r3/
*.dc.html
